    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a straightforward opportunity for a value-focused buyer who wants affordable transportation or a solid project platform. It offers a practical layout, a comfortable cabin, and the kind of usability that makes it easy to put to work right away. If you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive way to get into a vehicle with room to personalize and improve over time, this is a compelling option at an accessible price.",
