      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great option for someone who wants dependable, no-frills transportation or a solid project to tinker with. Easy on the wallet, straightforward, and priced to move \u2014 a practical choice if you need something affordable and usable without spending a fortune.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and a chassis that still feels planted on the road. Starts, moves, and stops, with good bones for someone who knows their way around maintenance and wants an affordable platform to build, daily, or restore. Shows wear consistent with age and use, but the fundamentals are there: responsive power delivery, usable interior, and plenty of potential left in the package. If you want an inexpensive driver/project with upside, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
