      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with undeniable presence, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads and sparks ideas. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for a hands-on driver, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for an affordable ride with personality to spare. There\u2019s a rugged charm here you just can\u2019t fake\u2014an opportunity to own something with soul at a budget-friendly price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
