      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. An honest opportunity for someone seeking an inexpensive car for local driving, a backup vehicle, or a project, it presents a practical way to get on the road without a big investment. If you want affordable ownership and understand the appeal of a value-focused purchase, this is well worth a look.",
